            "title": "盤中速報 - 威潤(6465)股價拉至漲停，漲停價49.05元，成交601張",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>威潤(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:6465:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6465\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6465-TW</a>)17日09:53上漲4.45元，股價漲停報49.05元，委買136,000張，成交601張。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>主要業務為衛星定位監控器之研發、製造及銷售。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>威潤(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:6465:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6465\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6465-TW</a>)近5日股價下跌4.09%，櫃買市場<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/TWS/TSE01\">加權指數</a>上漲6.83%，短期股價無明顯表現。</p></section><section><p><em>近5日籌碼</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>三大法人合計買賣超：-31 張</li> <li>外資買賣超：-17 張</li> <li>投信買賣超：0 張</li> <li>自營商買賣超：-14 張</li> <li>融資增減：+254 張</li> <li>融券增減：+1 張</li> </ul></section></main>",
